872
00:59:01,380 --> 00:59:02,711
Hassan!

873
00:59:03,780 --> 00:59:06,386
Mansur!

874
00:59:07,860 --> 00:59:09,100
Mahira!

875
00:59:11,740 --> 00:59:13,071
Mahira!

